```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Input Object] --> B{Is datetime.date or datetime.datetime?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Return obj.isoformat()]
    B -- No --> D{Is decimal.Decimal?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Return str(obj)]
    D -- No --> F[Raise TypeError]
